{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "apex", "namespace": "apex", "internal": "rig::ControlSpline", "icon": "APEX/rig-ControlSpline-", "version": "", "tags": "apex", "since": "20.0"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["rig::ControlSpline"], "extent": [141, 164]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Creates a spline of a given order using a list of CVs."], "extent": [164, 227]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The spline generated from the control matrices is a bezier curve of the specified ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["order"]}, ". This means that the number of control matrices must satisfy the equation, ", {"type": "code", "text": ["<number_of_cvs> % (order-1) == 1"]}, "."], "extent": [227, 431]}, {"level": 1, "id": "inputs", "container": true, "type": "inputs_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [431, 439], "body": [{"type": "inputs_item_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "inputs_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["cvs"], "role": "item", "extent": [439, 447], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The list of transforms that specify each CV\u2019s translate, normal (", {"type": "code", "text": ["N"]}, "), and tangent (", {"type": "code", "text": ["tangentu"]}, ") values. The transform is also written to the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["transform"]}, " attribute as a ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Matrix3"]}, " type."], "extent": [479, 668]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"type": "VariadicArg<Matrix4>"}}, {"ext": null, "type": "inputs_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["twists"], "role": "item", "extent": [668, 678], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Twist values (in radians) to write to the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["twist"]}, " point attribute. There does NOT have to be a twist value per CV. Twist values are interpolated linearly across the length of the spline."], "extent": [708, 900]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"type": "VariadicArg<Float>"}}, {"ext": null, "type": "inputs_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["order"], "role": "item", "extent": [900, 909], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The order of the generated spline curve."], "extent": [924, 970]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"type": "Int"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "text": "Inputs"}, {"level": 1, "id": "outputs", "container": true, "type": "outputs_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [970, 979], "body": [{"type": "outputs_item_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "outputs_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["geo"], "role": "item", "extent": [979, 987], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The output geometry containing the created spline."], "extent": [1007, 1063]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"type": "Geometry"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "text": "Outputs"}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [1063, 1072], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/apex/rig--ControlSplineFromArray-", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/apex/rig--ControlSplineFromArray-.html"}], "extent": [1072, 1115]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/apex/rig--SampleSplineTransforms-2.0", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/apex/rig--SampleSplineTransforms-2.0.html"}], "extent": [1115, 1161]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/apex/rig--SampleSplineTransformsToArray-2.0", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/apex/rig--SampleSplineTransformsToArray-2.0.html"}], "extent": [1161, 1214]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/apex/rig--SplineInterpolateTransforms-2.0", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/apex/rig--SplineInterpolateTransforms-2.0.html"}], "e